OL,3,CYearly water bills to rise by average
OL,4,Cof #123 from April, figures show
OL,6,FHouseholds in England and Wales will
OL,7,Fsee their yearly water bill rise by an
OL,8,Faverage of #123, or 26%, from April 1,
OL,9,Ffinal figures show.
OL,11,FThe rise, confirmed by industry body
OL,12,FWater UK, will take the average water
OL,13,Fand wastewater bill from #480 to #603
OL,14,Ffor the next year alone. This equates
OL,15,Fto an increase of around #10 a month,
OL,16,Ffrom #40 to #50.
