OL,4,Cof #123 from April, figures show
OL,6,FHowever, millions of households face
OL,7,Feven steeper rises, including Southern
OL,8,FWater customers, who will see a 47%
OL,9,Fincrease, bringing the supplier's
OL,10,Faverage yearly bill reaching #703.
OL,12,FHafren Dyfrdwy, South West Water and
OL,13,FBournemouth Water will all see a 32%
OL,14,Fincrease to their bills, while Thames
OL,15,FWater customers are warned of a 31%
OL,16,Fhike. Yorkshire Water is raising bills
OL,17,Fby 29%.
