OL,6,FThe Consumer Council for Water (CCW)
OL,7,Fsaid stronger and fairer support was
OL,8,Furgently needed to protect struggling
OL,9,Fhouseholds from the largest rise in
OL,10,Fwater bills since the privatisation of
OL,11,Fthe water industry 36 years ago.
OL,13,FWater UK said firms would invest
OL,14,Faround #20 billion from April 2025 to
OL,15,FMarch 2026, the highest ever level of
OL,16,Fexpenditure in a single year, and the
OL,17,Ffirst in a five-year programme of
OL,18,Finvestment worth #104 billion up to
OL,19,F2030.
