OL,6,FThe investment would help to build
OL,7,Fnine new reservoirs and nine new water
OL,8,Ftransfer schemes, upgrade the capacity
OL,9,Fof 1,700 wastewater treatment works to
OL,10,Freduce pollution and improve and
OL,11,Fprotect more than 15,000 kilometres of
